p: For Zika fever, 144 and 311 R-values ​​were generated for the years 2015 and 2016, respectively. For Chikungunya fever, 285 and 303 R-values ​​were generated for the years 2015 and 2016, respectively. For Dengue fever, 357 and 414 R-values were generated for the years 2015 and 2016, respectively.
